love letter to los angeles
EUROPE ! im doing my first headline tour this summer on your beautiful continent. playing all the greatest hits. tickets on sale now on my website.

traveled the country with my best friends. 33 shows in 51 days . i cannot begin to explain how much gratitude i have for everyone involved. i love you from the bottom of my heart and haven’t even scratched the surface on processing how lucky i am to have you all in my life. don’t know if i ever will. to everyone who came to a show, ur the reason and the reason alone i do this. Here Goes Nothing Tour is officially a wrap. im gonna go to the mountains and write some songs and miss every day of being on the road. you have my whole heart and i will see you all so soon. to all my touring friends, you inspire me everyday, whether that was the openers, the crews, the people who we left notes for in dressing rooms and the people who were on their own tour at the same time as us. this isn’t easy but god damn is it worth it. community is key and community is what we have. the fans who came to the show with their loved ones, the ones who came by themselves who made friends and the friends who came to the show who became fans,  seeing you all wrap your arms around each other and laugh and cry and sing put a million breaths into my lungs thank you thank you thank you x100 i’ll never be able to say it enough. europe you’re up next i will see u so soon!

BIGTIMEGOODTIME out tonight at 9pm pst!!!

this is one of my favorite songs i’ve ever written. it was a time i was endlessly scrolling and wondering why i was doing it so mindlessly so i just started listing things that freak me out. 

i was looking for a big time good time but really i was trying to distract myself from putting in the work on myself which gets me no where. no where fast. zoom zoom baby. 

all this pent up emotion led me to write the lyrics for this in a span of what felt like a couple minutes and i don’t think i’ve ever been more honest in a song. it’s happy it’s sad and it’s a little bit of everything in between. hope you love it ♥️
